cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper discusses the network architecture and emerging technologies for future wireless communication systems, which falls under the category of computer networks and communications (cs.NI). It also mentions the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and big data analytics (cs.MM) to assist in the development of 6G architecture. The paper also discusses the integration of wireless information and energy transfer (cs.IT) and the use of unmanned aerial vehicles (cs.RO) in 6G communication.
